{"tid":1747051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔係要泛民win 我係要建制輸","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:55:27.000Z","uid":153452,"like":128,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b0445b791429ed3dad4c8025bca8ee8e77e59b03","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"我唔係要泛民win 我係要建制輸 <br />\n大家要記住呢樣野<br />\n無論你幾憎泛民都好<br />\n都唔可以俾保皇黨win<br />\n你寧願食一舊美女既屎 定啊伯既爛屎？ 答案好撚簡單<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>總之 邊個投建制or 白票就係鬼！！！！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"dd20858eede3a1fe571b9791b9bcd3612b9c6ce3","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f05cd4181ee1b6e3b026658dcc610ff42b85db2d","tid":1747051,"uid":35084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ui2RDvo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUi2RDvo.jpg&h=ba93a272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4c12c81eb316cdae5b5f0c5d80f721c7ac749b0","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0a94170c1ae7831a5785149cd3f7331248b9f11","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63f026852518b09761b2168e3f045eba5572977b","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88e4a2a57dec2ccc018d95656997caf47d41e310","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ce18f4aa023de9a1a878b866ec63740b51e4144","tid":1747051,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=a518fe61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fn&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=c4f08234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/n</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期日0730 見)"},{"pid":"52357eeb343340f2fd06293bf413ca74a72fd55b","tid":1747051,"uid":153452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"18783c1dd8d28ad4